Class UpsightManagedFloat

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • com.upsight.android.managedvariables.internal.type.ManagedVariable<T>
        • com.upsight.android.managedvariables.type.UpsightManagedVariable<java.lang.Float>
          • com.upsight.android.managedvariables.type.UpsightManagedFloat

  • public abstract class UpsightManagedFloat
extends UpsightManagedVariable<java.lang.Float>
    A Float field with its value configurable through the Upsight Dashboard. This class extends an Observable so changes to its value can be monitored through adding an Observer to this class.
